      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * ACCA</b>\n</p><p><b>ACCA</b> - The Americas' Computer Chess Association.\n</p><p>The ACCA has membership that spans multiple countries in the Americas and sponsors The <i>Americas' Computer Chess League</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> which is a series of geographical on-line tournaments, notably the:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/ACCA_Americas%27_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"ACCA Americas&#39; Computer Chess Championship\">ACCA Americas' Computer Chess Championship</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ACCA_World_Computer_Rapid_Chess_Championship\" title=\"ACCA World Computer Rapid Chess Championship\">ACCA World Computer Rapid Chess Championship</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ACCA&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31506\">ACCA stance on Ippo, Robbo and such</a> by <a href=\"/Charles_Roberson\" title=\"Charles Roberson\">Charles Roberson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 06, 2010</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ACCA&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aigames.net/ACCA/tacca.html\">The Americas' Computer Chess Association</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aigames.net/ACCA/AmericasComputerChessLeague.html\">The Americas' Computer Chess League</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Americas\">Americas from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Americas\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Americas (orthographic projection).svg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ca/Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg/330px-Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg.png\" width=\"330\" height=\"330\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ca/Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg/500px-Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ca/Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg/960px-Americas_%28orthographic_projection%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ACCA&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aigames.net/ACCA/AmericasComputerChessLeague.html\">The Americas' Computer Chess League</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301014025\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.601 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node